You asked, we listened. We’ve made updates to help you boost your GPA:

Our brand new app-specific Help Center will include up-to-date FAQ and ways to contact us for 1:1 help.
We’ve got more updates coming soon! To make sure you don’t miss them, keep your Updates turned on.

Thanks for choosing Chegg!

We’re always working hard to help you boost your GPA by making regular updates:

-You asked for it and we responded. Your textbook solutions now sync between mobile and desktop!
-And that annoying thing in Textbook Solutions where you tap to go back and went all the way back to the home screen? We fixed that too.

We’ve got more updates coming soon. To make sure you don’t miss them, keep your Updates turned on.

Thanks for choosing Chegg!
